{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"dd266d1a63","title":"王洪文、张春桥在军委办公会议听取三总部汇报批林批孔运动情况时的插话（摘录）","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"5afe95008c","index":0,"year":1974,"month":2,"day":8,"articleId":"dd266d1a63"}],"tags":[{"id":"19f210967c","name":"总参谋部政治部","type":"出版方/发行方"},{"id":"4172b5fa3c","name":"九·一三事件","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"471a503675","name":"张春桥","type":"人物"},{"id":"8d506eedf8","name":"温玉成","type":"人物"},{"id":"8e2c446eb1","name":"王洪文","type":"人物"},{"id":"ad51b2eae3","name":"批林批孔","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[{"id":"b2387b1ed9","name":"王洪文、张春桥一九七四年二月八日在军委办公会议听取三总部汇报批林批孔运动情况时的插话（摘录）","articleId":"dd266d1a63"}],"publications":[{"id":"bd33de67-6641-49bc-a820-870b3a2aa3df","name":"“四人帮”罪行材料（九）（1977.1）","internal":true,"official":true,"type":"img","author":"总参谋部政治部，1977.1","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives1/main/bd33de67-6641-49bc-a820-870b3a2aa3df/1.png,https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives1/main/bd33de67-6641-49bc-a820-870b3a2aa3df/2.png,https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives1/main/bd33de67-6641-49bc-a820-870b3a2aa3df/3.png"}],"authors":[{"id":"b2b7bbb332","name":"王洪文"},{"id":"fae13ac6b9","name":"张春桥"}]},"publication_details":{"bd33de67-6641-49bc-a820-870b3a2aa3df":{"comments":[{"id":"b0116c0cf9","publicationId":"bd33de67-6641-49bc-a820-870b3a2aa3df","articleId":"dd266d1a63","index":-1,"part_index":-1,"offset":-1,"text":"总参谋部政治部，一九七七年一月"}],"contents":[{"id":"0696f99308","type":"title","text":"王洪文、张春桥一九七四年二月八日在军委办公会议听取三总部汇报批林批孔运动情况时的插话（摘录）","index":0,"publicationId":"bd33de67-6641-49bc-a820-870b3a2aa3df","articleId":"dd266d1a63"},{"id":"ef1e4f1a5d","type":"paragraph","text":"当总参仲华同志汇报时","index":1,"publicationId":"bd33de67-6641-49bc-a820-870b3a2aa3df","articleId":"dd266d1a63"},{"id":"3fc15f2270","type":"paragraph","text":"张春桥同志（下称张）：汇报不要照本子念。抓点，要首长自己抓。五十七张大字报，三万多分之五十七。主席讲批孔不是从七三年五月开始，以前不说，八届十二中全会即讲了。","index":2,"publicationId":"bd33de67-6641-49bc-a820-870b3a2aa3df","articleId":"dd266d1a63"},{"id":"f0fff36c1c","type":"paragraph","text":"当才千同志讲到阎仲川、温玉成问题未搞清时","index":3,"publicationId":"bd33de67-6641-49bc-a820-870b3a2aa3df","articleId":"dd266d1a63"},{"id":"15bc1a7d65","type":"paragraph","text":"张：你们很多问题都没有搞清。说不深不透，一点具体的不讲，张挺的问题我今天才听到。","index":4,"publicationId":"bd33de67-6641-49bc-a820-870b3a2aa3df","articleId":"dd266d1a63"},{"id":"9cf9e9fdc5","type":"paragraph","text":"当别的领导同志批评总参领导太软弱时","index":5,"publicationId":"bd33de67-6641-49bc-a820-870b3a2aa3df","articleId":"dd266d1a63"},{"id":"84d95cad2c","type":"paragraph","text":"张：你们的大事，光我知道的没有哪一件有结果的。如总参作战部有人跑到山东，跟袁升平一起骂浩亮，报告我逐段批，你们写了几页顶了回来，我不想管。艾玲的丈夫在你们二部，未解决嘛！上海给你们提供材料，你们一点不提供。知道的人不多，为什么不发动群众揭呢？","index":6,"publicationId":"bd33de67-6641-49bc-a820-870b3a2aa3df","articleId":"dd266d1a63"},{"id":"005bd5b95c","type":"paragraph","text":"王洪文（下称王）：她是有言论有行动。邱、李、叶在那里指挥干的。","index":7,"publicationId":"bd33de67-6641-49bc-a820-870b3a2aa3df","articleId":"dd266d1a63"},{"id":"0df1572396","type":"paragraph","text":"张：你们就说没事，到你们那里就说没事。","index":8,"publicationId":"bd33de67-6641-49bc-a820-870b3a2aa3df","articleId":"dd266d1a63"},{"id":"f3e8f64c05","type":"paragraph","text":"王：应该充分发动群众揭。","index":9,"publicationId":"bd33de67-6641-49bc-a820-870b3a2aa3df","articleId":"dd266d1a63"},{"id":"894a2deb21","type":"paragraph","text":"张：张挺翻案也未解决，不是下面的，你们几个怎么样？","index":10,"publicationId":"bd33de67-6641-49bc-a820-870b3a2aa3df","articleId":"dd266d1a63"},{"id":"49d9242f2a","type":"paragraph","text":"王：总参领导右，右得很。群众批评你们从“九·一三”以后一直被动，有道理。许多问题有题目，无下落。如温玉成、黄永胜，他们经营那么多年，不搞几个人依靠谁呀？","index":11,"publicationId":"bd33de67-6641-49bc-a820-870b3a2aa3df","articleId":"dd266d1a63"},{"id":"84a17008b7","type":"paragraph","text":"当别的领导同志问雷英夫怎样时","index":12,"publicationId":"bd33de67-6641-49bc-a820-870b3a2aa3df","articleId":"dd266d1a63"},{"id":"e06e612031","type":"paragraph","text":"王、张：关起来是一回事，要查清，不然关两年又放出来了。","index":13,"publicationId":"bd33de67-6641-49bc-a820-870b3a2aa3df","articleId":"dd266d1a63"},{"id":"3bd0e5c52b","type":"paragraph","text":"王：总参领导对批林整风领导不得力，很不得力。","index":14,"publicationId":"bd33de67-6641-49bc-a820-870b3a2aa3df","articleId":"dd266d1a63"},{"id":"40e7a66b18","type":"paragraph","text":"张：儿童团我还是第一次从贵部听到，我是反驳了的。五十年后主席、副主席都要从幼儿园找。你们这些问题未解决嘛！要研究、讨论、解决、落实。","index":15,"publicationId":"bd33de67-6641-49bc-a820-870b3a2aa3df","articleId":"dd266d1a63"},{"id":"5997ca170b","type":"paragraph","text":"王：批评是一回事，落实解决又是一回事。","index":16,"publicationId":"bd33de67-6641-49bc-a820-870b3a2aa3df","articleId":"dd266d1a63"},{"id":"bc5da1e411","type":"paragraph","text":"张：不抓大事不能光要你们负责，军委有责任，有些事可以这样说。你们的精神状态还有些问题，让群众推着走。","index":17,"publicationId":"bd33de67-6641-49bc-a820-870b3a2aa3df","articleId":"dd266d1a63"},{"id":"ac68e894b4","type":"paragraph","text":"当别的领导同志对总参运动作指示时","index":18,"publicationId":"bd33de67-6641-49bc-a820-870b3a2aa3df","articleId":"dd266d1a63"},{"id":"60f184d710","type":"paragraph","text":"张：要放手发动群众，不要怕，坏人利用要跳出来是好。要保证作战指挥。空军有些提法值得考虑。不算历史旧账，什么旧账？不要打横炮，遗留问题向上写小字报。总参情况你（指才千同志）是否有数？我看你也不一定比我知道的多。","index":19,"publicationId":"bd33de67-6641-49bc-a820-870b3a2aa3df","articleId":"dd266d1a63"}],"page":{"id":"b2e62d9687","publicationId":"bd33de67-6641-49bc-a820-870b3a2aa3df","articleId":"dd266d1a63","start":2,"end":3}}}},"__N_SSG":true}